CasparCG Client
===============

Thank you for your interest in the CasparCG Client, a Mac/Windows/Linux client 
software used to control graphics, audio and video playout and recording
by the CasparCG Server software.

This release is considered tested and stable, and is intended for use in
professional production.


SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS FOR WINDOWS
-------------------------------

The Windows version has been tested on Windows 10 x64. 
No extra installations required.


SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS FOR MAC
---------------------------

The Mac version has been tested on 11.
No extra installations required.


SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS FOR LINUX
-----------------------------

The Linux version has been tested on Ubuntu 22.04 64-bit.
Requires that you install VLC.


INSTALLATION WINDOWS
--------------------

No installation required, just move the program to a suitable location and 
start it.


INSTALLATION MAC
----------------

Open the DMG file and drag the 'CasparCG Client' app to your Applications
folder.


INSTALLATION LINUX
------------------

Install the deb file, and launch 'CasparCG Client'


DOCUMENTATION
-------------

Ask questions in the forum: http://casparcg.com/forum.


